translated: Jönsson, Emanuel, postmaster. Färjestaden, born on 27/11/91 in Munkaljungby, Kriist. 1., the son of Sven J. and Anna Kristina KHnker. Married on 23 to Anna EmiHa Paulina Andersson. Completed his secondary education in Halmstad in 1910. Worked as a postal clerk in the western district from 1913, in a post office there from 1917, in Höganäs from 1919, as a postal inspector there from 1925, in Hälisingb. from 1934, first postal inspector in Lidköp. from 1937, and postmaster in Färjestaden since 1944. Married.
